original_title: Animals Are Amazing: Untamed Africa: Part One
overview: Emmy Award-winner John Hurt narrates world-renowned wildlife filmmaker Frederic LePage's breathtaking chronicle of one of nature's most awe-inspiring migrations, as hundreds of thousands of wildebeests and zebras embark on their treacherous trek toward the Masai Mara in Kenya.
title: Animals Are Amazing: Untamed Africa: Part One
